==Engish==

===Verb===
'''[[take]] [[into]] [[account]]'''

#{{idiom}} To [[consider]] or [[regard]]; to [[include]] (as in an estimate or plan) or pay [[attention]] to; to [[notice]].
#:''His plan did not '''take into account''' the possibility of rain.''
